Wild Fusion is an African digital marketing agency founded in 2010 by Abasiama Idaresit
Wild Fusion services include media planning and buying (including digital, mobile, direct and search), digital marketing, online marketing, consumer insights, media strategy, creative, social media marketing and technology development. With operations in Nigeria, Ghana and Kenya, Wild fusion services local African clients in these markets. Some of Wild fusion's clients include Unilever (Nigeria and Ghana), Vodacom, Diamond Bank, Planned Parenthood and more African and international clients.
Partner businesses include ROI Digital (online media sales house)and Wild Fusion Digital Centre (WDC) the company's digital marketing training institute. Wild Fusion Digital Centre is the Nigerian local training centre for the Digital Marketing Institute of Ireland.
In April 2016, Wild Fusion was awarded the Brand Development Awards at the inaugural Mobile West African Awards
